docs {
  # ExportReady.AI - Modul 2: Manajemen Produk & AI Services
  
  ## PBI Coverage:
  - **PBI-BE-M2-01**: GET /products - List products dengan pagination
  - **PBI-BE-M2-02**: GET /products/:id - Get product detail
  - **PBI-BE-M2-03**: POST /products - Create new product
  - **PBI-BE-M2-04**: PUT /products/:id - Update product
  - **PBI-BE-M2-05**: DELETE /products/:id - Delete product
  - **PBI-BE-M2-06**: AI HS Code Mapper (via Kolosal AI)
  - **PBI-BE-M2-07**: AI Description Rewriter (via Kolosal AI)
  - **PBI-BE-M2-08**: AI SKU Generator
  - **PBI-BE-M2-09**: POST /products/:id/enrich - Trigger AI Enrichment
  
  ## How to Use:
  1. Run requests in order (Auth Flow first)
  2. Tokens are automatically saved to variables
  3. Test AI enrichment on different product types
  
  ## Kolosal AI Integration:
  - Model: Claude Sonnet 4.5
  - Features: HS Code generation, B2B Description, SKU generation
}
